'''Trustant''' was the title given to the [[Caamasi/Legends|Caamasi]] who led the individual [[Caamasi Remnant]] communities. The Trustant was responsible for maintaining the community's ways, in the hope of one day returning to [[Caamas/Legends|Caamas]], destroyed by the agents of [[Palpatine/Legends|Emperor Palpatine]] after the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]].

